cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this knowledge graph, adapter or code, please cite it as below."
title: "CodeFeedback-KG: A Semantic Educational Knowledge Graph with GraphRAG for Programming Feedback"
abstract: >-
  An Educational Knowledge Graph for introductory Python (OWL 2 RL closure, SHACL
  shapes, SKOS, and skos:exactMatch links to Wikidata) used as the retrieval
  substrate for a GraphRAG programming-feedback pipeline, together with a QLoRA
  fine-tuned adapter and a human-grounded criterion-validity study of an LLM judge.
type: software
authors:
